{"tid":2167749,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"推警員胸口 15歲少年遭蘇文隆還柙","createTime":"2020-08-21T10:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T20:32:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"85671fe2119de20f194b4ba06e1b4eae05656381","tid":2167749,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:02:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/W4HEQVP2RRFIZNLIUTNNZKPM5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FW4HEQVP2RRFIZNLIUTNNZKPM5E%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu6DV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=39cba97f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FW4HEQVP2RRFIZNLIUTNNZKPM5E%2F&h=d3a381b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/W4HEQVP2RRFIZNLIUTNNZKPM5E/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年聖誕節各區均有「和你shop」行動，有市民於沙田新城市廣場聚集及叫口號。15歲男生被指當日在警方防線前推警員胸口，今在粉嶺法院少年法庭承認襲警罪。辯方求情指，男生家住沙田，當日在朋友影響下前往現場，因見大批防暴警員，在不知所措下「揈手揈腳」，誤傷警員，強調絕非故意推撞或衝擊。主任裁判官蘇文隆將少年還柙至下月11日判刑，其間為他索取社會福利、感化、勞教中心、更生中心及青少年罪犯評估專案小組報告。<br />\n<br />\n辯方強調，被告當日只是跟隨朋友到現場，被捕時身上沒任何常見的示威裝備，案發片段亦沒看到他施襲。辯方冀法庭念在被告初犯，加上他已承諾不再參與社會運動，可先索取感化報告再判刑，並相信其間沒需要將被告還柙。惟蘇官最終將被告男生還柙候判。"},{"pid":"94604da5430f11c8cdcbdfb0124e09b00e62ee65","tid":2167749,"uid":80851,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"又係蘇文隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90867398887d24316ce8207a7103e557c35ae21","tid":2167749,"uid":47202,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:06:52.000Z","msg":"見到蘇文隆呢條冚家剷就知會點判啦dllm"},{"pid":"7a5c5a02916d8286ae45dd626c35f6de9518516c","tid":2167749,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94604da5430f11c8cdcbdfb0124e09b00e62ee65","tid":2167749,"uid":80851,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"又係蘇文隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\